Description: Removing sample locations south of Point Sur where quillback rockfish are not found
Removing sampling before 2014 prior to the first full coverage of the state in the first super year 2015 ( 2014-2016)
Relegating the depth range of the analysis to within 110 m depth range where quillback rockfish were observed by the ROV
Removal of any sites where only soft bottom was indicated by GIS layers for seafloor type
